				<wikidot:authorName>Asdfaslas</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5335699</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Anafabula itself causes not only the erasure of the infected texts, but the removal of memory of ever knowing about or discussing the texts after a while. So it could have been the Foundation getting rid of some of the books, but that last comment was a natural consequence of the last-described book.</p> 
				 	]]>
