				<wikidot:authorName>al90</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5337654</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So basically&#8230;</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;probably&nbsp;wrong</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The anafabula ate another anomaly (the books), this poster had noticed, and the Foundation hijacked his account as part of a plot to discredit it all as a hoax and cover it up?</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Whether or not that’s close to what’s actually going on here, this is really great. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
