				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12280243#post-4324006</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12280243/scared-stiff#post-4324006</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2019 22:50:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Oboebandgeek99</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1782920</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Bandwagon: Jumped upon<br /> Draft: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">cold</span>lukewarm posted<br /> Parawatch: [DATA EXPUNGED]</p> <p><em><strong>I am forcibly removed from the SCP Wiki.</strong></em></p> </blockquote> <p>This is my <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">ripoff</span> love letter to Candle Cove and other creepypastas that led me to this site. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gee0765" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5376871&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1567124639" alt="gee0765" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5376871)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gee0765" >gee0765</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1567124639" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" >Crashington</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1567124639" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span> for looking over this.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Hints/Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li>The Foundation is really good at covering things up.</li> <li>There are two anomalies at play here, one intentional, and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2747">one that crept in</a> due to the kind of narratives Scared Stiff told.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p><strong>Translations:</strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-887480-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup><br /> <a href="http://lafundacionscp.wikidot.com/scared-stiff">Muerto de Miedo</a> on SCP-ES translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/morhadow" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3535580&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1567124639" alt="morhadow" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3535580)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/morhadow" >morhadow</a></span><br /> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scared-stiff">呆若木雞</a> on SCP-CN translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4357011&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1567124639" alt="feitag" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4357011)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" >feitag</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-887480-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. this thing has translations now what???</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
